<id>http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=17&amp;p=71#p71</id>
<link href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=17&amp;p=71#p71"/>
<title type="html"><![CDATA[Here's how to view them]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=17&amp;p=71#p71"><![CDATA[
In order to see this document, follow these directions.<br /><br />1. go to <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.ipdl.jpo.go.jp/homepg_e.ipdl">http://www.ipdl.jpo.go.jp/homepg_e.ipdl</a><!-- m --><br />2. click on Patent &amp; Utility Model Gazette DB<br />3. Enter Kind Code: A<br />4. Enter Number: S55-096186<br />5. click on search, a link to document JP,55-096186,A(1980) will appear in a pane on the left.  click it<br />6. You will be told that the document is not available in English, so Click on the button that says JAPANESE.<br /><br />If anyone can make sense of it, please post the info on these boards.  The pictures themselves are somewhat revealing, even with the japanese captions.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=29">teaguecl</a> — Thu Oct 21, 2004 5:28 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
